This is just an remake of the orginal TwoTowers, Same like the remakes "2009" "night" "32" Now we made the "DoubleTrouble"

We made it 2 towers each spawn within each tower 2 sniper platforms, In the middle are fake boxes where you can hide it and the looks are made from stone,

Also the weapons on the wooden wall from the original "m4a1" ( ct side ) "Ak-47" ( T side ) are gone and the weapons on both spawn in the water are gone "Mp-5"

We did this cause people would make adventages of it and would try to reach those weapons as first, then they would swim back up and end up with an bullet right between there eyes.

So for those issues we deleted the weapons and just make this map fight for your lives and kill the tower campers.

I got board one night and started another map. I just went with the flow again. This is only 2-3 days of work. A preview of the construction can be found here. Youtube time lapse. There are two versions of this map. This is the snow version that has it snowing with snow on the ground and the other one has it raining. Teams spawn on opposite sides of the map. The layout is balanced to where both sides are identical but the trees are a bit off. The lower level of the map has crates and a small water area. Zip file includes .nav file

Map Author: ShadowChild aka [PT] ShadowChild aka Skint aka Skint26

Description:  Just a simple fightyard I used to play with my old clan a few years back.  Good Times.  If you're one of those 24/7 Iceworld kind of guys/gals you'll have some good fun with this map.

It's nothing spectacular in the way of graphics or anything, but the gameplay is fun.  There may be some issues here and there, but nothing that would ruin the fun that I'm aware of.  We ran it on a no camping server, and it was a blast.  I'm sure some will love it, and others will hate it. Works for me. :)

Copyright notice?  You're kidding right?  Have at it if you want to do anything with it... it could be easily re-created by most of the mappers here anyway.

Haven't mapped in years so don't expect any edits or updates, just sharing the fun.

ABOUT THE RELEASE: This is the Alpha release of my concept map, fy_tripview. ================================================= ABOUT THE MAP: Max Players: 32 slots Ideal Players: 16 The map consists of three levels with one hallway, The hallway's floors and ceilings are made of bulletproof glass, so you always know where your enemies are, but what can you do to get to them? It is a phychological map and requires you to use team communication to kill your enemies. So how good is your clan's communication? ================================================= Contents of this Package : fy_tripview.BSP ================================================= Installation Instructions : Unzip contents Copy "cstrike" into C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\YOURNAME\counter-strike source\ ================================================= <<< M3-Knifely >>> Please leave me some feedback at my email : M3knifely@gmail.com Game On
